Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.19,0:00:07.35,Saku-main,RITA,0000,0000,0000,,It's the last painting Mashiro \Ndid before she came to Japan.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.04,0:00:10.99,Saku-main,RITA,0000,0000,0000,,Has this helped you understand...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.93,0:00:13.25,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,Mashiro a little better?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.80,0:00:15.91,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Shiina should...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.07,0:00:19.52,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,return to the world of fine arts.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.90,0:01:56.01,Eptitle,EPTITLE,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(900,1)}#10 Hate Hate, Love
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.45,0:02:09.42,Saku-main,RITA,0000,0000,0000,,You're not making any progress, Sorata.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.42,0:02:11.49,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,It has nothing to do with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.49,0:02:14.14,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, I thought you \Nmoved into Shiina's room.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.14,0:02:16.57,Saku-main,RITA,0000,0000,0000,,Mashiro's working, so I \Ncame in here to play.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.85,0:02:19.36,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,I'm working too, you know...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.36,0:02:21.28,Saku-main,RITA,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.66,0:02:23.52,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,I'm drawing storyboards for Nyapollon.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.52,0:02:25.11,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,I'm diagramming the camera blocking.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.61,0:02:29.74,Saku-main,RITA,0000,0000,0000,,Are you visualizing the final \Nproduct while you're drawing?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.49,0:02:32.54,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,No, I'm just guessing really...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.92,0:02:33.79,Saku-main,RITA,0000,0000,0000,,Let me see that.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.83,0:02:39.25,Saku-main,RITA,0000,0000,0000,,You have your reference right \Nin front of you, so look at it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.25,0:02:41.14,Saku-main,RITA,0000,0000,0000,,You have to look at it \Nwhile you're drawing.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.57,0:02:42.55,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Rita-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.11,0:02:44.97,Saku-main,RITA,0000,0000,0000,,Just watch.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.15,0:02:54.90,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,You're really good...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.20,0:02:57.90,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.09,0:03:00.32,Saku-main,RITA,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.48,0:03:03.27,Saku-main,RITA,0000,0000,0000,,You must have it rough.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.27,0:03:04.07,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.60,0:03:07.58,Saku-main,RITA,0000,0000,0000,,Both Mashiro's and Misaki's \Nwork are incredible.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.43,0:03:11.30,Saku-main,RITA,0000,0000,0000,,Working alongside people who are bursting...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.30,0:03:15.42,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,at the seams with talent \Nmust be quite a burden.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.45,0:03:21.24,Saku-main,RITA,0000,0000,0000,,Have you made up your mind...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.24,0:03:23.33,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,about Mashiro returning to England yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.29,0:03:29.19,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,If you're telling me to talk \Nto her, it's no good.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.19,0:03:30.43,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,She won't listen to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.90,0:03:33.76,Saku-main,RITA,0000,0000,0000,,Either way, I think you'd be more effective...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.76,0:03:35.96,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,in persuading her than I would be.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.97,0:03:39.64,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,I want to ask you something.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.06,0:03:41.21,Saku-main,RITA,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.92,0:03:43.14,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,What did you mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.14,0:03:45.32,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,when you said Shiina would destroy me?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.95,0:03:48.35,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Does it have anything to do with \Nwhy you stopped painting?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.56,0:03:53.62,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Rita's in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.04,0:03:57.00,Saku-main,RITA,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. I was deepening my \Nfriendship with Sorata.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.00,0:03:59.00,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Don't say it like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.40,0:04:01.59,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,You're finished?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.06,0:04:05.47,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,What did Misaki-senpai say?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.90,0:04:07.18,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,She hugged me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.18,0:04:08.68,Saku-thought,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,I love you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.68,0:04:09.97,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,...is what she said.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.97,0:04:11.89,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Must be perfect, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.49,0:04:13.69,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Is it okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.69,0:04:15.90,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I think it's perfect, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.04,0:04:53.02,Saku-main,RITA,0000,0000,0000,,Good evening.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.33,0:04:56.94,Saku-main,AKASAKA,0000,0000,0000,,Don't expect to have \Neverything your way, freeloader.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.64,0:04:59.40,Saku-main,RITA,0000,0000,0000,,What are you trying to say?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.75,0:05:02.90,Saku-main,AKASAKA,0000,0000,0000,,I'm saying that Kanda still has \Nthat which you've forgotten.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.51,0:05:06.48,Saku-main,RITA,0000,0000,0000,,You seem to have me all figured out.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.48,0:05:08.43,Saku-main,AKASAKA,0000,0000,0000,,You've already given up on art.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.49,0:05:11.74,Saku-main,AKASAKA,0000,0000,0000,,That's all I needed to \Nknow to figure you out.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.79,0:05:14.26,Saku-main,RITA,0000,0000,0000,,You were listening?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.69,0:05:17.50,Saku-main,RITA,0000,0000,0000,,A gentleman doesn't eavesdrop.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.07,0:05:36.08,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Kanda-kun, have you been working too hard?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.08,0:05:38.77,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,No, I just haven't slept very well recently.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.77,0:05:41.45,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Rita came to bother me again last night.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.85,0:05:43.89,Saku-main,AKASAKA,0000,0000,0000,,I don't like that girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.89,0:05:47.03,Saku-main,AKASAKA,0000,0000,0000,,Just looking at her fake \Nsmile makes me angry.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.03,0:05:48.07,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Her fake smile?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.07,0:05:49.28,Saku-main,AKASAKA,0000,0000,0000,,What's on today's agenda?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.03,0:05:52.21,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,We've actually run into \Na bit of a problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.64,0:05:54.46,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,If we want to participate \Nin the culture festival,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.46,0:05:56.29,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,the Student Council is \Ninsisting that a representative...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.29,0:05:57.77,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,makes a presentation.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.77,0:05:58.58,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,A presentation?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.81,0:05:59.53,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.00,0:06:01.74,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,We have to explain what we're going to do,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.74,0:06:03.26,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,not just to the Student Council,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.26,0:06:04.84,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,but to the festival committee...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.84,0:06:06.76,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,and the student union, as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.15,0:06:09.64,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,This is a job for the director, Sorata.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.64,0:06:10.78,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.78,0:06:12.99,Saku-main,AKASAKA,0000,0000,0000,,I have something to report, as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.12,0:06:16.86,Saku-main,AKASAKA,0000,0000,0000,,The art for the dramatic sequences \Nis two days behind schedule.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.86,0:06:19.14,Saku-main,AKASAKA,0000,0000,0000,,At this rate, we won't make \Nit in time for the festival.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.14,0:06:19.98,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,I'll do my best.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.98,0:06:21.92,Saku-main,AKASAKA,0000,0000,0000,,You're already producing work...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.92,0:06:23.65,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,with astounding speed and quality.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.41,0:06:26.08,Saku-main,AKASAKA,0000,0000,0000,,It would be unrealistic for you...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.08,0:06:27.78,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,to shoulder more work alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.30,0:06:30.64,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like it's my time to shine!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.64,0:06:32.83,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to help you, Mashiron!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.17,0:06:34.76,Saku-main,AKASAKA,0000,0000,0000,,Kamiigusa-senpai, your modeling work...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.76,0:06:36.29,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,is all that you have room for.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.73,0:06:38.05,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,Then, we'll increase our numbers!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.05,0:06:39.97,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll invite more people \Nto join our merry band!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.97,0:06:43.67,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think anyone at school \Nwill associate with Sakura Hall.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.89,0:06:48.17,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,It's all because the storyboards \Nare falling behind schedule.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.53,0:06:50.20,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,Don't sweat it, kouhai-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.20,0:06:52.05,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,That's right. \NSlow and steady wins the race.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.42,0:06:54.42,Saku-main,AKASAKA,0000,0000,0000,,But if we can't meet our deadlines,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.42,0:06:57.31,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,it won't matter how \Npolished our work is.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.31,0:07:06.41,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,Student Council President.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.61,0:07:09.40,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,Hau-hau's here, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.10,0:07:12.25,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, everyone! This is the girl who's...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.25,0:07:14.13,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,providing the music for Nyapollon!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.13,0:07:16.24,Saku-main,HAUHAU,0000,0000,0000,,Please don't call me that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.24,0:07:18.16,Saku-main,HAUHAU,0000,0000,0000,,My name is Himemiya Saori.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.47,0:07:20.79,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,Are you eating lunch together?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.79,0:07:22.56,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,You two sure are close.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.61,0:07:25.34,Saku-main,TATEBAYASHI,0000,0000,0000,,Did you get our message, Mitaka?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.34,0:07:26.74,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,About the presentation?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.21,0:07:29.48,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't it a little unfair that \Nwe're the only group...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.48,0:07:30.93,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,that has to do one?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.93,0:07:32.50,Saku-main,TATEBAYASHI,0000,0000,0000,,Suimei High's culture festival...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.50,0:07:35.62,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,is a major event for the neighborhood, \Nspanning an entire week.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.62,0:07:37.85,Saku-main,TATEBAYASHI,0000,0000,0000,,We get a lot of outside interest.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.35,0:07:39.46,Saku-main,TATEBAYASHI,0000,0000,0000,,Instead of complaining,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.46,0:07:41.19,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,try reflecting on the way \Nyou conduct yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.19,0:07:42.89,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be such a stuffed shirt.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.89,0:07:44.27,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,We've known each other a long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.51,0:07:46.57,Saku-main,TATEBAYASHI,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, involuntarily.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.80,0:07:49.99,Saku-main,TATEBAYASHI,0000,0000,0000,,Class is starting. Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.57,0:07:51.37,Saku-main,HAUHAU,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.71,0:07:53.57,Saku-main,HAUHAU,0000,0000,0000,,See you later.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.86,0:07:59.79,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,That was the Student Council President?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.79,0:08:02.09,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,That's Tatebayashi Soichiro-senpai.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.67,0:08:05.58,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Jin-san, you don't get along with him?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.58,0:08:08.07,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,It's not intentional on my part.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.07,0:08:11.74,Saku-main,AKASAKA,0000,0000,0000,,At any rate, this'll be a \Ndifficult obstacle to overcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.92,0:08:22.24,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe me being the director \Nwasn't such a good idea...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.24,0:08:23.88,Saku-main,AKASAKA,0000,0000,0000,,If that's what you think, just quit.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.88,0:08:24.83,Saku-main,AKASAKA,0000,0000,0000,,I don't need someone...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.83,0:08:26.40,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,who's afraid of a little \Nwork ordering me around.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.40,0:08:28.17,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Akasaka-kun, don't you\N think you should...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.17,0:08:29.85,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,choose your words a \Nlittle more carefully?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.85,0:08:34.51,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,On top of that, can you kindly refrain \Nfrom eating tomatoes during class?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.51,0:08:36.69,Saku-main,AKASAKA,0000,0000,0000,,Don't bring up such irrelevant topics.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.69,0:08:38.14,Saku-main,AKASAKA,0000,0000,0000,,Just so you know,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.14,0:08:40.74,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,I have greater faith in tomatoes \Nthan in anything else in the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.40,0:08:44.27,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,We have to increase our numbers.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.64,0:08:47.55,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Let's look for people who \Ncan rival Shiina's talent.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.55,0:08:49.91,Saku-main,AKASAKA,0000,0000,0000,,Easier said than done. Not many people...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.91,0:08:51.56,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,can produce work of the same quality.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.56,0:08:52.34,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,There is one.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.71,0:08:54.60,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Rita.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.18,0:08:57.09,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Do you think she'll help us?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.40,0:08:59.81,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,She told me she gave up on art.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.81,0:09:01.96,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Rita would never give up on art.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.96,0:09:02.90,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.58,0:09:05.10,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Rita loves art.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.17,0:09:08.27,Saku-main,AKASAKA,0000,0000,0000,,She's certainly talented.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.11,0:09:10.27,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.65,0:09:12.32,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,She's already a professional artist?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.44,0:09:15.21,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,You didn't see them?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.59,0:09:16.28,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,See what?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.57,0:09:18.99,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Rita's paintings were at the exhibition.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.99,0:09:19.78,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.99,0:09:19.78,Saku-overlap,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,You're kidding!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.99,0:09:24.31,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,What were you two looking at?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.02,0:09:27.67,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Rita.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.23,0:09:31.14,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Rita!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.00,0:09:33.57,Saku-main,RITA,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, welcome home.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.99,0:09:36.63,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Rita, I have a favor to ask you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.23,0:09:39.35,Saku-main,RITA,0000,0000,0000,,Do you want me to take \Nyou back to England?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.72,0:09:42.14,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Draw Nyapollon with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.95,0:09:45.79,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,We don't have enough people,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.79,0:09:49.07,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,and nobody else can match\N the quality of Shiina's work.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.07,0:09:51.86,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Shiina said you'd be able to do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.86,0:09:53.32,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,I'd appreciate your help, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.40,0:09:56.29,Saku-main,RITA,0000,0000,0000,,I'll have to decline.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.79,0:09:59.09,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not as good as Mashiro.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.09,0:10:00.32,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,That's not true.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.76,0:10:02.31,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,You're a good artist.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.35,0:10:09.65,Saku-main,RITA,0000,0000,0000,,Please stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.65,0:10:11.74,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,I've already decided never to draw again.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.22,0:10:14.18,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.94,0:10:16.65,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,You're a great artist.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.75,0:10:24.74,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Rita?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.02,0:10:28.56,Saku-main,RITA,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be ridiculous.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.13,0:10:31.86,Saku-main,RITA,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be ridiculous.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.99,0:10:36.74,Saku-main,RITA,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to hear those \Nwords from you of all people.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.99,0:10:38.17,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.63,0:10:44.30,Saku-main,RITA,0000,0000,0000,,Whose fault do you think it \Nis that I gave up on art?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.15,0:10:46.91,Saku-main,RITA,0000,0000,0000,,It's all {\i1}your{\i0} fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.98,0:10:51.98,Saku-main,RITA,0000,0000,0000,,Do you remember the other children...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.98,0:10:54.55,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,who came to my grandfather's studio?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.96,0:11:01.50,Saku-main,RITA,0000,0000,0000,,Did you notice how they \Ndisappeared, one by one?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.49,0:11:06.93,Saku-main,RITA,0000,0000,0000,,You probably don't even remember \Ntheir names or their faces.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.94,0:11:10.33,Saku-main,RITA,0000,0000,0000,,You only ever looked \Nat your own paintings.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.17,0:11:13.27,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.82,0:11:18.02,Saku-main,RITA,0000,0000,0000,,They all grew to hate the art \Nthey'd so loved because of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.63,0:11:20.41,Saku-main,RITA,0000,0000,0000,,They couldn't even stand to look at...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.41,0:11:21.45,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,a canvas or a pencil anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.33,0:11:28.75,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,It's my fault?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.75,0:11:30.23,Saku-main,RITA,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.23,0:11:31.67,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter how hard I tried,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.67,0:11:33.25,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't measure up to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.25,0:11:37.23,Saku-main,RITA,0000,0000,0000,,It makes me realize what\N it means to have true talent.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.09,0:11:42.70,Saku-main,RITA,0000,0000,0000,,After ten years, I was the only one left.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.62,0:11:45.82,Saku-main,RITA,0000,0000,0000,,You'd swept them all away.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.32,0:11:47.89,Saku-main,RITA,0000,0000,0000,,Unaware and apathetic,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.55,0:11:50.60,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,you didn't care that\N everyone had left.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.13,0:11:55.36,Saku-main,RITA,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't forgive you \Nfor being that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.50,0:11:58.22,Saku-main,RITA,0000,0000,0000,,I wished you'd just disappear...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.22,0:12:00.04,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,that you'd go somewhere far away...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.04,0:12:02.20,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,so I helped you become a manga artist.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.09,0:12:05.14,Saku-main,RITA,0000,0000,0000,,I figured you deserved a life\N of drawing boring manga,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.54,0:12:07.38,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,and ruining your own reputation,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.87,0:12:11.22,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,so you could understand \Na little of what we felt.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.78,0:12:13.99,Saku-main,RITA,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.34,0:12:17.83,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,But why did you have\N to make your debut?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.83,0:12:19.13,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Rita?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.57,0:12:23.31,Saku-main,RITA,0000,0000,0000,,I want you to become the \Nworld's most famous painter.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.84,0:12:29.14,Saku-main,RITA,0000,0000,0000,,You could have at least \Nlet me brag someday...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.14,0:12:32.10,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,that I once studied at \Nthe same studio with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.58,0:12:36.12,Saku-main,RITA,0000,0000,0000,,I want to think I'm a part of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.69,0:12:39.69,Saku-main,RITA,0000,0000,0000,,I want to believe I exist \Ninside your talent.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.68,0:12:43.78,Saku-main,RITA,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure Sorata doesn't \Nunderstand how I feel.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.99,0:12:50.33,Saku-main,AKASAKA,0000,0000,0000,,Did you get everything \Noff your chest, freeloader?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.73,0:12:52.20,Saku-main,AKASAKA,0000,0000,0000,,If you're done, budge.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.71,0:12:54.08,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,You're in the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.08,0:12:56.83,Saku-main,AKASAKA,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks to you, we've lost \Nprecious work time.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.83,0:12:59.28,Saku-main,RITA,0000,0000,0000,,You could have just walked past me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.28,0:13:00.98,Saku-main,AKASAKA,0000,0000,0000,,I hate women.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.98,0:13:03.30,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,I avoid being near them \Nas much as humanly possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.30,0:13:06.93,Saku-main,RITA,0000,0000,0000,,You recluse types with computerized \Nfriends sure do think differently.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.24,0:13:09.48,Saku-main,AKASAKA,0000,0000,0000,,I trust computers,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.48,0:13:12.85,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,and I am objectively aware \Nthat I am a recluse.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.28,0:13:15.21,Saku-main,AKASAKA,0000,0000,0000,,If that was meant as an insult,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.21,0:13:18.11,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,your mind is further gone \Nthan I can possibly fathom.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.11,0:13:19.74,Saku-main,RITA,0000,0000,0000,,Don't mock me!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.74,0:13:21.17,Saku-main,AKASAKA,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not mocking you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.17,0:13:23.14,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,I just think you're a coward.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.55,0:13:25.73,Saku-main,AKASAKA,0000,0000,0000,,Smiling those stupid fake smiles.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.73,0:13:27.67,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,Imagine how we must feel...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.67,0:13:29.41,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,looking at your depressing face.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.78,0:13:32.56,Saku-main,RITA,0000,0000,0000,,How do you think I feel when I smile?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.08,0:13:35.84,Saku-main,RITA,0000,0000,0000,,Creating art was my world!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.84,0:13:37.76,Saku-main,RITA,0000,0000,0000,,Ever since I can remember,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.76,0:13:40.17,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,I've always been told that\NI would be a fantastic artist!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.71,0:13:43.17,Saku-main,RITA,0000,0000,0000,,But my grandfather told \Nme to stop trying.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.68,0:13:45.53,Saku-main,RITA,0000,0000,0000,,I could never outdo Mashiro \Nso I should just stop...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.53,0:13:47.43,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,There was no point in \Ncontinuing to paint!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.77,0:13:49.89,Saku-main,RITA,0000,0000,0000,,I know it's cowardly to cling to Mashiro...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.89,0:13:51.60,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,even after being told that!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.95,0:13:53.47,Saku-main,RITA,0000,0000,0000,,It's all Mashiro's fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.47,0:13:54.56,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,It's her fault for existing!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.26,0:13:56.27,Saku-main,AKASAKA,0000,0000,0000,,I have one question.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.51,0:13:59.98,Saku-main,AKASAKA,0000,0000,0000,,Where was your will in that story?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.56,0:14:01.44,Saku-main,RITA,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.02,0:14:03.99,Saku-main,AKASAKA,0000,0000,0000,,I understand that people around you...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.99,0:14:06.95,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,had high expectations, \Nand you failed to meet them.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.80,0:14:12.65,Saku-main,AKASAKA,0000,0000,0000,,But you don't seem to have \Nexplained what {\i1}you{\i0} want.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.52,0:14:17.89,Saku-main,RITA,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you taking such \Nenjoyment from analyzing people?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.89,0:14:19.34,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,You're a jerk!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.34,0:14:19.88,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Rita!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.24,0:14:21.36,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Rita-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.13,0:14:24.12,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Akasaka, let's go after her!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.47,0:14:25.87,Saku-main,AKASAKA,0000,0000,0000,,You go after her.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.87,0:14:27.82,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be more effective.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.82,0:14:30.06,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,You really shouldn't do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.06,0:14:31.86,Saku-main,AKASAKA,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure I don't know what you mean.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.51,0:14:33.80,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Spouting your mouth off...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.80,0:14:35.20,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,when you don't actually care...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.20,0:14:36.66,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,what happens to other people!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.54,0:14:51.12,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Where did she go?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.12,0:14:53.64,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know. We just have to look...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.75,0:14:55.80,Saku-overlap,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Rita hates me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.29,0:14:58.36,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Shiina?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.16,0:15:04.88,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't understand anything she said.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.95,0:15:09.84,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Sorata, do you understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.84,0:15:16.51,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Shiina, have you ever envied anyone?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.51,0:15:17.97,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Envied?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.38,0:15:19.85,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Have you ever thought \Nsomeone was great,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.85,0:15:21.84,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,or someone was amazing,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.84,0:15:24.25,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,or looked up to someone?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.38,0:15:26.28,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.44,0:15:28.26,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.33,0:15:31.61,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Kanda-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.22,0:15:45.19,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.06,0:15:50.42,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,had a vague feeling \Nthat Shiina was alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.15,0:15:53.01,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,That no one could enter her world.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.17,0:15:56.84,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,The other art students are \Nall curious about her,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.84,0:15:58.56,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,but they keep their distance.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.58,0:16:02.53,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Shiina probably doesn't \Nhave any close friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.14,0:16:05.63,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,But you're different.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.06,0:16:07.68,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,You reach Shiina.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.28,0:16:11.14,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Your words, your heart, \Nyour very existence.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.85,0:16:13.70,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,There's a lot she doesn't understand,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.34,0:16:16.66,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,but I'm certain that you're \Nvery important to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.38,0:16:18.62,Saku-main,RITA,0000,0000,0000,,You really think so?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.91,0:16:23.08,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,I think it's amazing you were \Nwith her for ten years.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.72,0:16:25.32,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Any normal person would have run away.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.14,0:16:28.30,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,A normal person looks away from \Nwhat they don't want to see.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.03,0:16:31.32,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Even if they know there are things...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.32,0:16:33.77,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,they can only acquire if they \Nface the things they hate.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.91,0:16:37.65,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,I want to become someone \Nwho can do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.65,0:16:38.51,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Someone like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.78,0:16:42.39,Saku-main,RITA,0000,0000,0000,,Did you come to console me?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.92,0:16:45.60,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,At first, that was my intent, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.81,0:16:49.07,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,What type of smile is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.64,0:16:51.80,Saku-main,RITA,0000,0000,0000,,Probably still a fake one.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.20,0:16:55.20,Saku-main,RITA,0000,0000,0000,,It looks like that boy knew \Nfrom the very beginning.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.97,0:17:02.20,Saku-main,RITA,0000,0000,0000,,He's right, you know. \NI've forgotten what I want to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.67,0:17:03.54,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.69,0:17:07.50,Saku-main,RITA,0000,0000,0000,,I still think his personality stinks, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.93,0:17:10.84,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Making something with talented people...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.84,0:17:13.47,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,like Shiina and Misaki-senpai is difficult.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.42,0:17:17.59,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,It's difficult, but it's \Nalso really exciting.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.27,0:17:20.59,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,I learn things just watching them,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.59,0:17:22.27,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,and watching an amazing \Nproduct take shape...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.27,0:17:24.77,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,before my eyes is \Nan astonishing experience.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.66,0:17:28.36,Saku-main,RITA,0000,0000,0000,,That's how you see things?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.98,0:17:30.48,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.53,0:17:40.36,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.09,0:17:42.20,Saku-main,RITA,0000,0000,0000,,You didn't know what?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.62,0:17:45.03,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't know what you were thinking.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.00,0:17:47.33,Saku-main,RITA,0000,0000,0000,,How about now?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.16,0:17:49.25,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.70,0:17:52.17,Saku-main,RITA,0000,0000,0000,,I expected that. \NThat's just who you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.86,0:17:54.51,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't notice at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.04,0:17:56.76,Saku-main,RITA,0000,0000,0000,,That's what I don't like about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.34,0:18:00.70,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Because I had so much fun...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.70,0:18:02.37,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,drawing next to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.64,0:18:07.02,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,I felt like I wasn't alone \Nwhen I was with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.81,0:18:11.90,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,I only needed you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.09,0:18:16.61,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,But I was the only one having fun...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.00,0:18:19.77,Saku-main,RITA,0000,0000,0000,,That's... That's not true!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.77,0:18:21.28,Saku-main,RITA,0000,0000,0000,,I had fun, as well!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.02,0:18:22.87,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Rita?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.65,0:18:29.99,Saku-main,RITA,0000,0000,0000,,It wasn't just you. I had fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.99,0:18:31.72,Saku-main,RITA,0000,0000,0000,,I kept creating art to this very day...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.72,0:18:34.34,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,because I really enjoyed \Npainting with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.71,0:18:36.76,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.09,0:18:38.37,Saku-main,RITA,0000,0000,0000,,It's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.37,0:18:41.16,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted to keep creating \Nart with you forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.16,0:18:45.21,Saku-main,RITA,0000,0000,0000,,But I always thought \Nyou didn't even notice me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.35,0:18:48.02,Saku-main,RITA,0000,0000,0000,,When it crossed my mind \Nthat it was only me...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.02,0:18:50.82,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,who considered us \Nfriends, I was afraid...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.82,0:18:52.29,Saku-main,RITA,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't help it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.86,0:19:02.67,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Rita, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.67,0:19:05.13,Saku-main,RITA,0000,0000,0000,,Mashiro... Mashiro...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.23,0:19:07.62,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.99,0:19:10.17,Saku-main,RITA,0000,0000,0000,,I want to keep creating art.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.17,0:19:11.82,Saku-main,RITA,0000,0000,0000,,I want to take everything...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.82,0:19:13.73,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,I did with you and make art.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.33,0:19:15.84,Saku-main,RITA,0000,0000,0000,,The moments I spent with you...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.84,0:19:18.13,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,are my most treasured.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.69,0:19:20.67,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.67,0:19:22.79,Saku-main,RITA,0000,0000,0000,,Mashiro, I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.54,0:19:25.35,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Rita, you should make your own art.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.20,0:19:39.35,Saku-thought,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.35,0:19:42.74,Saku-thought,,0000,0000,0000,,Making something with \Nsomeone else is fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.40,0:19:47.74,Saku-thought,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Sometimes it'll bring you down, \Nbut that's only natural.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.37,0:19:51.58,Saku-thought,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,After all, I don't have \Nany skills or experience.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.26,0:19:55.09,Saku-thought,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Rita and Shiina spent \Nten years together.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.67,0:19:57.94,Saku-thought,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,She was overwhelmed by Shiina's talent,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.94,0:20:00.22,Saku-thought,,0000,0000,0000,,but she kept trying hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.85,0:20:02.77,Saku-thought,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Compared to her,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.77,0:20:05.82,Saku-thought,,0000,0000,0000,,I've only known Shiina for half a year.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.46,0:20:08.30,Saku-thought,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Getting depressed and \Nlosing my confidence...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.30,0:20:11.07,Saku-thought,,0000,0000,0000,,when nothing has happened\N would be shameful of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.46,0:20:15.06,Saku-thought,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay. We can do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.58,0:20:18.09,Saku-thought,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,If the residents of Sakura \NHall work together,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.09,0:20:20.05,Saku-thought,,0000,0000,0000,,we can create something amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.18,0:20:24.01,Saku-thought,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Shiina's not alone anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.58,0:20:27.21,Saku-thought,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,We're all friends working \Ntowards a common goal.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.01,0:20:31.87,Saku-thought,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,I'll do everything I possibly can.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.86,0:20:36.38,Saku-thought,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,So I can get just a little \Ncloser to reaching Shiina...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.25,0:20:46.14,Sign,SIGN,0000,0000,0000,,Welcoming Rittan and Presenting Nyapollon\N at the Culture Festival Celebration
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.76,0:20:40.93,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,After some minor delays, \Nlet the "Welcoming Rittan...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.93,0:20:43.76,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,and Presenting Nyapollon at the...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.76,0:20:46.14,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,Culture Festival Celebration" begin!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.14,0:20:48.31,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! We did it, Rittan!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.53,0:20:47.93,Saku-overlap,RITA,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.31,0:20:50.12,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,We did it, Nyapollon!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.31,0:20:50.12,Saku-overlap,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,We should be thanking you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.12,0:20:51.67,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,With your help, \Nwe won't have any reason...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.67,0:20:53.27,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,to worry about our schedule.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.71,0:20:55.27,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,I can't wait to see the final product.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.59,0:20:57.69,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,I'll work hard on learning my lines.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.69,0:20:59.90,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Sorata, good job.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.84,0:20:59.91,Saku-overlap,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,Look forward to it, Nanamin!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.90,0:21:03.83,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Th-Thanks. Why the mushroom?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.91,0:21:02.16,Saku-overlap,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,I've prepared an ultra-cute cat suit!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.16,0:21:03.66,Saku-overlap,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,A cat suit?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.83,0:21:04.73,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,It's a gift.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.73,0:21:06.51,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,You just didn't want it, did you?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.51,0:21:09.20,Saku-main,AKASAKA,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think I really \Nneed to be here...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.20,0:21:09.91,Saku-main,RITA,0000,0000,0000,,Ryunosuke.{
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.88,0:21:12.61,Saku-main,RITA,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry about the other day.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.61,0:21:13.68,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,I spoke too rashly.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.68,0:21:15.96,Saku-main,AKASAKA,0000,0000,0000,,Acknowledging your \Nmistakes is a virtue.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.32,0:21:19.55,Saku-main,RITA,0000,0000,0000,,I finally understand what \Nyou were trying to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.12,0:21:23.22,Saku-main,RITA,0000,0000,0000,,Sorata really does have \Nwhat I had forgotten.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.50,0:21:24.74,Saku-main,AKASAKA,0000,0000,0000,,Don't stand so close to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.74,0:21:25.59,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,It's giving me the willies.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.15,0:21:28.35,Saku-main,RITA,0000,0000,0000,,You really do hate girls, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.86,0:21:32.61,Saku-main,RITA,0000,0000,0000,,I want to know what \Nkind of person you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.11,0:21:35.44,Saku-main,AKASAKA,0000,0000,0000,,K-Kanda! Change seats with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.19,0:21:37.15,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,What's your problem?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.11,0:21:43.03,Sign,SIGN,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for Coming!!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.52,0:21:44.44,Saku-main,RITA,0000,0000,0000,,Sorata.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.44,0:21:45.17,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.64,0:21:47.53,Saku-main,RITA,0000,0000,0000,,I still haven't changed my mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.15,0:21:51.48,Saku-main,RITA,0000,0000,0000,,I think Mashiro should paint \Ninstead of drawing manga.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.27,0:21:56.78,Saku-main,RITA,0000,0000,0000,,But I'll behave myself until \Nthe culture festival.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.53,0:22:00.42,Saku-main,RITA,0000,0000,0000,,I want to see Nyapollon \Ncompleted, as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.94,0:22:02.07,Saku-main,BOTH,0000,0000,0000,,Rita...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.43,0:22:07.13,Saku-main,RITA,0000,0000,0000,,I love making art.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.35,0:22:10.83,Saku-main,RITA,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Sorata.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.60,0:22:13.24,Saku-main,RITA,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Mashiro.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.61,0:23:33.88,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,The culture festival... \NWhat a lively event.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.82,0:23:40.98,NextEptitle,TEXT,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(458,1)}#11 Milky Way Cat, Nyapollon
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.28,0:23:38.03,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,Girls from other schools come \Nand play with Suimei girls.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.03,0:23:40.98,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,But this year's culture festival \Nwill be difficult and energetic.
